his agreement shall be governed and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Texas, without giving effect to any conflicts of law provisions</p>\n<p><strong>Binding Effect</strong> This Agreement shall be binding upon the parties hereto and their respective successors and permissible assigns.</p>\n<p>User agrees to be bound by these terms and conditions, by using AHI’s website.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]</p>\n','TERMS AND CONDITIONS','','inherit','closed','closed','','283-autosave-v1','','','2020-07-29 04:59:04','2020-07-29 04:59:04','',283,'http://188.166.160.223/american/283-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(306,1,'2020-07-29 04:59:20','2020-07-29 04:59:20','[vc_section el_class=\"who-we-are-sec\"][vc_row el_class=\"container align-center\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\"][vc_column_inner css=\".vc_custom_1595847985841{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1595853268879{margin-bottom: 15px !important;padding-right: 35px !important;}\" el_class=\"welcome-head\"]\r\n<h2><b>Certified Hotel General Manager (CHGM)</b></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text el_class=\"certification-points\"]\r\n\r\nThe Certified Hotel General Manager (CHGM) certification is for hospitality general managers and department heads who have achieved expertise in hotel operations leadership and who possess the required experience or education.\r\n\r\nRequirements:\r\n<ul class=\"pointed-finger\">\r\n 	<li>2 years of college education or 1 year of relevant work experience</li>\r\n 	<li>A passing score on the CHGM exam</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTo APPLY, send an email with CHGM in the subject line to <a href=\"info@americanhospitality.institute\">info@americanhospitality.institute</a>, and attach your resume.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]','Certified Hospitality Gene